<https://w3id.org/noria/instances/TroubleTicketNote/TTN-20240420-001-01> a noria:TroubleTicketNote ;
  rdfs:label "Initial diagnosis for TT-20240420-001"@en ;
  rdfs:comment "First note on the high CPU incident. Initial investigation shows high CPU on DBServer01. No immediate cause found. Escalating to DB Admin Team."@en ;
